Among auto-HCT patients, no child died of viral infection. For allo-HCT patients, a CMV-IgG positive recipient with ALL as primary disease was a risk factor for death (HR=1.5; 
 p=0.045) in multivariate analysis. Other risk factors for death were MUD vs MSD (HR=2.3; 
 p=0.049) and MMUD vs MSD (HR=3.8; 
 p<0.001) (
